abstract: >-
  OSIRIS: Sovereign quantum computing framework with 8-qubit DNA-encoded
  registers (qByte system), genetically evolved Living Language Model (LivLM),
  Non-Causal Living Model (NCLM) for quantum text generation, 9-agent NCLLM
  deliberation swarm, Bayesian cognitive mesh governance, tridirectional
  introspection engine, adversarial bridge validator, CRSM 7D torsion physics,
  FABRIC NSF testbed integration, Quantum-to-Matter 3D manufacturing pipeline,
  and automated Zenodo publishing. 25+ CLI commands, zero external LLM
  dependencies, pure NumPy quantum execution. Co-authored by devin phillip
  davis and OSIRIS dna::}{::lang NCLM.
